Interface PersonApiMapper

All Known Implementing Classes:
PersonApiMapperImpl
public interface PersonApiMapper

Person API Mapper

MapStruct mapper for transforming domain models to API DTOs and vice versa. Bridges internal domain models with external REST API representations, handling field name mappings and structure transformations.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jakub Pavlíček
